text: Recreate zipper branch off 2.0
Merge coverage support.
First version of Hypothesis tests for the zipper; unfinished, but works well enough to find some bugs
Merge testdata changes and Parameter nodes into zipper.
Revise zipper tests for speed and to be more accurate about what is being tested
Replace None with Empty in the ASTs and refactor the zipper tests to work with this
Add the remaining parts of the traversal API and tests for it
Add comments and docstrings to the zipper and the tests
Fully move tests to unittest and fix minor test issues
Start zipperification of the rest of the project, fix util.singledispatch to work with the zipper
Improve zipper's backwards compatibility and fix bugs
Clean up some comments and docstrings
Make the field character limit for __str__ a global constant
Clean up spacing, typos, and add .hypothesis to .gitignore
Add infer(), frame(), scope(), and statement() methods to the zipper
